{"body": "Sprockets is going to be a dependency to Action Pack in the same way that Active Record is a dependency to Rails. Yes, it should be technically possible to separate the two, but it shouldn't be surfaced as an option in the same way that Sass is. So that means it's not going to go into the user-generated Gemfile.\r\n\r\nAlso, less dramatic grandstanding will increase the likelihood that your arguments will be given a fair hearing. (This includes tweets like \"look I made a scene with DHH in a pull request, come watch!\").", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/1446576", "created_at": "2011-06-27T11:10:29Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/1855#issuecomment-1446576", "updated_at": "2011-06-27T11:10:29Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 1855, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/dhh/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/dhh/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/dhh/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/dhh", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/dhh/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/dhh", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/dhh/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://1.gravatar.com/avatar/ed9635566b34ade32274f510f0f9a6d2?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2Fcdcb2f5c7b071143529ef7f2705dfbc4.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/dhh/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/dhh/received_events", "gravatar_id": "ed9635566b34ade32274f510f0f9a6d2", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/dhh/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "dhh", "type": "User", "id": 2741, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/dhh/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "52384d2bbd3543c151011493"}, "id": 1446576, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/1855"}
